00:01:06.630 --> 00:01:09.430
It's a stunning landscape.

00:01:09.430 --> 00:01:14.560
The watershed is one of the
most healthy salmon watersheds

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:16.530
in all of North America.

00:01:16.530 --> 00:01:19.160
Most watersheds can only handle
one or two species of salmon.

00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:22.115
But Taku has all five
species of salmon.

00:01:26.850 --> 00:01:29.420
What that means
for our fishery is

00:01:29.420 --> 00:01:33.810
that we can provide commercially
viable salmon sustainably

00:01:33.810 --> 00:01:37.130
harvested for five to six
months out of the year.

00:01:37.130 --> 00:01:41.330
There's almost no other river
system that you can do that.

00:01:41.330 --> 00:01:45.065
The inlet itself is stunning.

00:01:45.065 --> 00:01:46.490
Absolutely stunning.

00:01:46.490 --> 00:01:48.320
I love the quote, the
silence is deafening.

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:57.260
You want people
to taste the smell

00:01:57.260 --> 00:02:01.380
of Alaska, the fresh
ocean air, the stillness.

00:02:01.380 --> 00:02:03.954
To be humbled by the
quality of what is here.

00:02:10.724 --> 00:02:12.390
What Taku River Red
had done differently

00:02:12.390 --> 00:02:20.310
on the boats is everything to
the fish by proper handling,

00:02:20.310 --> 00:02:21.760
making sure that
the fish are not

00:02:21.760 --> 00:02:26.760
bound by gravity, rapid
chilling, getting the blood out

00:02:26.760 --> 00:02:29.870
is key, and we do that
with a hypodermic needle.

00:02:29.870 --> 00:02:33.110
And we actually pump the
blood out within moments

00:02:33.110 --> 00:02:36.160
of the fish coming on board.

00:02:36.160 --> 00:02:39.270
It's the blood that
makes fish taste fishy.

00:02:39.270 --> 00:02:40.020
It's not the meat.

00:02:40.020 --> 00:02:41.290
It's just the blood.

00:02:41.290 --> 00:02:44.750
So we want to get the blood
out before it coagulates deep

00:02:44.750 --> 00:02:46.970
inside the capillaries.

00:02:46.970 --> 00:02:48.810
I want you to taste a sockeye.

00:02:48.810 --> 00:02:51.240
I want you to taste a coho.

00:02:51.240 --> 00:02:54.150
I want you to taste a king
and know the difference.

00:02:54.150 --> 00:02:58.410
And you can tell that
by removing the blood.

